  <name>Scrolex</name>
  <summary>A horizontally scrolled PDF viewer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Scrolex is a PDF viewer that lays pages out along a single horizontal
      strip, letting you scroll continuously through a document. It supports
      zooming, including Ctrl+scroll and touchpad gestures, and text search.
    </p>
  </description>
